Introduction

Lovelyz is a eight-member girl group formed by Woollim Entertainment. They held their debut showcase on November 12, 2014 and released their first studio album "Girls' Invasion" on November 17.

On November 1, 2021, Woollim Entertainment announced 7 of the members, except Baby Soul, had chosen not to renew their contracts which expired on November 16. The group is currently on indefinite hiatus, with the members pursuing solo activities.

On August 28, 2024 it was announced that Lovelyz will release a new song for their 10th debut anniversary.
